Season: 2000-2001 Spring

*Promotion Playoff
*(between winter (Aguascalientes) and summer (La Piedad) champions 2nd level)
*[May 31] 
*Aguascalientes   1-0 La Piedad 
*[Jun 3] 
*La Piedad        4-1 Aguascalientes 
*
*La Piedad promoted

*Promotion/Relegation Playoff
*(between worst team 1st level and financially strong (5 million USD) team 2nd level)
*Fist Leg [Jun 6] 
*Veracruz         0-0 Atlante 

Leg: 2

*Atlante          4-1 Veracruz 
*  [Paulo Serafin 16, Manuel Sol 30, Jose Manuel Abundis 57, Jose Manuel Abundis 62; 
*   Guillermo Hernandez 51] 
*Atlante remain at 1st level
*NB: following the playoff, Irapuato's franchise was moved to Veracruz,
*    so Veracruz will play instead of Irapuato in 2001/02.

